## Lab 1 – Virtual Pet Generator
Student Name: Hiyaben Hareshbhai Jayswal
Enrollment Number: 200578344
Subject Code: COMP1073-26W-21138

## Objective
Create an interactive webpage that generates a random virtual pet. Users can change the pet’s name, age, and hunger status, and see the profile update immediately.

## Features
Random pet type, age, mood, and favorite activity
Update pet name using input
Increase or decrease pet age with buttons
Toggle hunger status (hungry / not hungry)
Fun description updates dynamically

## How It Works
Variables store pet information: petName, petType, petAge, isHungry, favoriteActivities, mood
Random values are generated using Math.random() and Math.floor()
JavaScript updates the webpage dynamically whenever the user changes the name, age, or hunger
